Revision history for Perl extension PDF::API2::Koromo

0.00_09 2012-12-02 23:32
        - fixed parameter "linewidth" handling in ->roundrect()

0.00_08 2012-12-02 18:35
        - fixed code in ->text()

0.00_07 2012-12-02 18:11
        - ->text() can be passed "auto_break" parameter
        - fixed code in ->text()

0.00_06 2012-12-01 10:57
        - fixed line-breaking in ->text()
        - ->text() can be passed "char_spacing" parameter, specifies space
          between characters

0.00_05 2012-11-30 19:30
        - in ->mm(), ->pt() and ->to_px(), fixed problem that error occurs when
          they are passed decimal parameter

0.00_04 2012-11-29 11:08
        - ->new() can be passed "file" parameter, like PDF::API2->new(file => $file)
        - ->importpage() can be passed path string to source PDF-file

0.00_03 2012-11-28 17:20
        - ->image() can fetch from web, passing parameter "url" (requires Furl)
        - added PDF::API2::Koromo::Types for type definition
        - added some tests
        - refactored

0.00_02 2011-05-16 08:45
        - requires Class::Accessor::Lite, insted of Class::Accessor::Faster
        - requires Data::Validator
        - refactored a little

0.00_01 2011-05-16 02:15
        - original version (ported from Hoya::X::PDF)
